I told my dad I wouldn’t be able to make it for Holi and his Birthday this year because i had a lot of work and tickets are costly, little did he know i had booked flights for this surprise 3 months in advance 🥰 
He kept telling everyone how his day was made because i came back home to surprise him ❤️🧿
Will be on my next trip before all these singapore pictures get posted 🥲🥰
